<style>
.peptides-reviews {
  background: #ffffff !important;
  padding: 6rem 0;
}

.peptides-reviews__title {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #111111 !important;
  margin: 0 0 3.2rem;
  text-align: center;
}

@media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
  .peptides-reviews__title {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
  }
}

.peptides-reviews__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
}

@media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
  .peptides-reviews__grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
}

.peptides-reviews__card {
  background: #ffffff !important;
  border: 1px solid #e5e5e5 !important;
  border-radius: 12px !important;
  padding: 28px !important;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.2rem;
  box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06) !important;
}

.peptides-reviews__rating {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.peptides-reviews__rating-score {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #111111;
}

.peptides-reviews__stars {
  color: #F5C518 !important;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  line-height: 1;
}

.peptides-reviews__card-title {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #111111 !important;
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.peptides-reviews__text {
  font-size: 14px !important;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: #444444 !important;
  margin: 0;
  flex: 1;
}

.peptides-reviews__footer {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-top: 0.4rem;
  border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  padding-top: 1.2rem;
}

.peptides-reviews__name {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #111111 !important;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin: 0;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

.peptides-reviews__badge {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #1a5c2e !important;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.peptides-reviews__badge-icon {
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
  background: #1a5c2e;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.peptides-reviews__badge-icon svg {
  width: 9px;
  height: 9px;
  fill: none;
  stroke: #ffffff;
  stroke-width: 2.5;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
}
</style>

<div class="peptides-reviews page-width">
  <h2 class="peptides-reviews__title">Wat onze klanten zeggen</h2>
  <div class="peptides-reviews__grid">

    <div class="peptides-reviews__card">
      <div class="peptides-reviews__rating">
        <span class="peptides-reviews__rating-score">5.0</span>
        <span class="peptides-reviews__stars" aria-label="5 sterren">★★★★★</span>
      </div>
      <p class="peptides-reviews__card-title">8 kilo kwijt in 8 weken</p>
      <p class="peptides-reviews__text">Na jaren worstelen met mijn gewicht besloot ik het anders aan te pakken. Binnen 8 weken was ik 6 kilo kwijt zonder mezelf uit te hongeren. Ik voel me energieker dan ooit en mijn eetlust is eindelijk onder controle. Had dit veel eerder moeten proberen.</p>
      <div class="peptides-reviews__footer">
        <p class="peptides-reviews__name">Linda V.</p>
        <p class="peptides-reviews__badge">
          <span class="peptides-reviews__badge-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
          Geverifieerde koper
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="peptides-reviews__card">
      <div class="peptides-reviews__rating">
        <span class="peptides-reviews__rating-score">5.0</span>
        <span class="peptides-reviews__stars" aria-label="5 sterren">★★★★★</span>
      </div>
      <p class="peptides-reviews__card-title">Twee maten kleiner na 10 weken</p>
      <p class="peptides-reviews__text">Mijn broek zit na 10 weken twee maten kleiner. Ik was sceptisch maar de resultaten spreken voor zich. Gecombineerd met wat meer bewegen ben ik 9 kilo afgevallen. De levering was supersnel en discreet verpakt, precies wat ik nodig had.</p>
      <div class="peptides-reviews__footer">
        <p class="peptides-reviews__name">Mark de B.</p>
        <p class="peptides-reviews__badge">
          <span class="peptides-reviews__badge-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>
          Geverifieerde koper
        </p>
